#include<iostream>
#include<cstdio>
#include<cstdlib>

using namespace std;

int main()
{

   int t,a,n,f,angle;
   cin>>t;

   while(t--)
   {

     cin>>a;

     n=3;

     f=0;

     while(1)
     {

        angle=(n-2)*180/n;

        if(angle==a)
        {
          f=1;
          break;
        }

        else if(angle > a)  break;

        n++;

     }

     if(f==0) cout<<"NO\n";

     else cout<<"YES\n";

   }

   return 0;

}
